OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1771879287
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe disappearance scenarios
OL,4,Cconsidered by police
OL,6,FA schoolboy who was found in a storm
OL,7,Fdrain could have hurt his head falling
OL,8,Foff his bicycle, an inquest jury has
OL,9,Fheard.
OL,11,FIt was among a number of scenarios
OL,12,Fthat were considered by detectives
OL,13,Finvestigating the disappearance of
OL,14,FNoah Donohoe in north Belfast in June
OL,15,F2020.
OL,17,FBrenda Campbell KC, counsel for Noah's
OL,18,Fmother Fiona Donohoe, said Noah was
OL,19,Fthe centre of a high-risk missing
OL,20,Fperson investigation and his behaviour
OL,21,Fhad "cried out for an explanation".
OL,26,@}D@EOU}D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
