FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1771879287
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe disappearance scenarios
OL,4,Cconsidered by police
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Gardner, who was
OL,7,Fthe CCTV co-ordinator in the
OL,8,Finvestigation, said detectives were
OL,9,Fstarting from Northwood Road ` the
OL,10,Flast sighting of Noah ` and working
OL,11,Fbackwards in their efforts to trace
OL,12,Fmaterial relating to the missing boy.
OL,14,FHe recalled that at one point "it was
OL,15,Fa considered hypothesis that he had a
OL,16,Fhead injury" after Noah had fallen off
OL,17,Fhis bike.
OL,26,@vD@_OUxD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
