FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1771879287
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe disappearance scenarios
OL,4,Cconsidered by police
OL,6,FThe inquest at Belfast coroner's court
OL,7,Finto the death of the schoolboy, which
OL,8,Fis being heard with a jury, is in its
OL,9,Ffifth week.
OL,11,FNoah, a pupil at St Malachy's College,
OL,12,Fwas 14 when his naked body was found
OL,13,Fin a storm drain tunnel in north
OL,14,FBelfast six days after leaving home on
OL,15,Fhis bike to meet two friends in the
OL,16,FCavehill area of the city.
OL,18,FOfficers were deployed on the ground
OL,19,Fto find CCTV that Noah appeared on.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1771879287
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe disappearance scenarios
OL,4,Cconsidered by police
OL,6,FMs Campbell KC questioned the officer
OL,7,Fon the use of CCTV in the missing
OL,8,Fperson investigation, including the
OL,9,Fneed for immediate trawls for footage,
OL,10,Fseizing key images quickly, how this
OL,11,Fmaterial fitted in with other lines of
OL,12,Finquiry and ensuring that the timings
OL,13,Fon the material was accurate.
OL,15,FMr Gardner said he would have expected
OL,16,Fofficers to "time-check and seize" the
OL,17,Frelevant footage, and the primary aim
OL,18,Fwas to try and find Noah.
OL,26,@xD@MOUxD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
