PN,44305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1771879287
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe disappearance scenarios
OL,4,Cconsidered by police
OL,6,FMs Campbell described Noah as
OL,7,F"vulnerable" at the time and said his
OL,8,Fappearance in Northwood Road meant
OL,9,Fthat something had gone wrong on his
OL,10,Fjourney.
OL,12,FShe told the officer: "Firstly, he had
OL,13,Fhis laptop, his backpack, at one
OL,14,Fstage, and not at another.
OL,16,F"You also knew by the time you came in
OL,17,Fon the Wednesday that his phone had
OL,18,Fbeen found in a separate location.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@LO]tD@WOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1771879287
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe disappearance scenarios
OL,4,Cconsidered by police
OL,6,F"There was a suggestion that he had
OL,7,Ffallen from his bike with no
OL,8,Fexplanation as to why he had fallen
OL,9,Ffrom his bike.
OL,11,F"His coat appeared to have been
OL,12,Fdiscarded in that area where he had
OL,13,Ffallen off his bike but it had not
OL,14,Fbeen found.
OL,16,F"You also knew that from there he
OL,17,Fproceeded up Northwood Road and items
OL,18,Fof his clothing were found on
OL,19,FNorthwood Road, and you knew that he
OL,20,Fwas last seen naked.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1771879287
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe disappearance scenarios
OL,4,Cconsidered by police
OL,6,F"Not only did we need to find him
OL,7,Fbecause of that level of vulnerability
OL,8,Fthat he was in, but what happened to
OL,9,Fhim cried out for an explanation."
OL,11,FMr Gardner responded: "Yes, if indeed
OL,12,Fsomething did happen to him."
OL,14,FOn a possible police hypothesis as to
OL,15,Fwhy he was behaving like that on
OL,16,FNorthwood Road, Mr Gardner said the
OL,17,Fonly thing he recalls is a discussion
OL,18,Fat one point about a possible injury.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@bO]sD@WOUtD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1771879287
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe disappearance scenarios
OL,4,Cconsidered by police
OL,6,FHe said: "I believe, after we had
OL,7,Flearned he had fallen off his bike, it
OL,8,Fwas a considered hypothesis he had a
OL,9,Fhead injury, but that was just because
OL,10,Fwe had heard he had fallen off his
OL,11,Fbike."
OL,13,FMr Gardner said he was not aware of
OL,14,Fany other hypothesis about why Noah
OL,15,Fbehaved that way he did in Northwood
OL,16,FRoad, "beyond, obviously, the concerns
OL,17,Fabout his mental wellbeing before he
OL,18,Fleft the house."
OL,20,FMs Campbell said there was no evidence
OL,21,Fof blood on Noah's top.
OL,26,@nD@JOUsD@FO]xD@GOUzD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/9
