FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1771879287
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe disappearance scenarios
OL,4,Cconsidered by police
OL,6,FNoah's helmet was recovered by police
OL,7,Fand it was undamaged, the court heard.
OL,9,FMr Gardner said "the objective was
OL,10,Fprimarily to find him (Noah)" and then
OL,11,Ftry to get information on how he
OL,12,Fbecame parted from his possessions
OL,13,Fsuch as his coat, backpack and phone.
